<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome Onboard!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: rgb(77, 175, 214);
            color: whitesmoke;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 26px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .otp-box { 
            background: rgb(226, 234, 238); 
            border: 2px solid rgb(56, 157, 252); 
            padding: 25px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center; 
            margin: 20px 0; 
        }

        .otp { 
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700; 
            color: #38b6ff; 
            letter-spacing: 3px; 
            padding: 15px; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: #fff; 
            margin: 10px 0; 
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #f0f4f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .highlight-box h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background: #0077cc;
            color: whitesmoke;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            padding: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome Aboard</h1>
            <p>Your account has been successfully created, you just have one step left, verify your email address.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We're thrilled to have you join our community! You're all set to explore everything we have to offer.</p>
            <p>to continue please verify your email below</p>


            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h2>Your Account Details</h2>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong>
                    <%= email %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Registration Date:</strong>
                    <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric' , month: 'long' , day: 'numeric' }) %>
                </p>
            </div>

            <center>
            <div class="otp-box">
                <h2>Verify your email address</h2>
                <div class="otp">
                    <%= otp %>
                </div>
                <p>This OTP will expire in 10 minutes. copy this to verify your email address</p>
            </div>
            </center>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h3>Security Tips</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Keep your password safe and don't share it</li>
                    <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
                    <li>Contact support if you notice suspicious activity</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>Thank you for choosing our platform!</p>
        <p>If you didn't create this account, please contact us immediately.</p>
        <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SkyTech. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>

</html>